<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Graduation Ceremony Invitation</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            background-color: #f8f9fa;
            color: #333333;
            line-height: 1.6;
        }
        .container {
            max-width: 600px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            background: white;
            box-shadow: 0 5px 15px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);
        }
        .header {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #0d47a1, #1565c0, #1976d2);
            color: white;
            padding: 30px 20px;
            text-align: center;
        }
        .content {
            padding: 40px 30px;
        }
        .footer {
            background-color: #0d47a1;
            color: #ecf0f1;
            padding: 25px 30px;
            text-align: center;
            font-size: 14px;
        }
        .button {
            display: block;
            width: 250px;
            background: linear-gradient(to right, #4CAF50, #2E7D32);
            color: #ffffff;
            text-decoration: none;
            font-weight: 600;
            font-size: 16px;
            padding: 16px 0;
            text-align: center;
            border-radius: 50px;
            margin: 30px auto;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 15px rgba(76, 175, 80, 0.3);
        }
        .event-details {
            background-color: #f0f7ff;
            border-radius: 10px;
            padding: 25px;
            margin: 30px 0;
            border-left: 5px solid #1976d2;
        }
        .icon-row {
            display: flex;
            margin-bottom: 12px;
        }
        .icon {
            color: #1976d2;
            margin-right: 15px;
            font-size: 18px;
            min-width: 24px;
        }
        .divider {
            height: 3px;
            background: linear-gradient(to right, transparent, #1976d2, transparent);
            margin: 30px 0;
        }
        .social-icon {
            display: inline-block;
            margin: 0 10px;
            color: #ffd700;
            text-decoration: none;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <center style="width: 100%;">
        <table align="center" border="0" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" width="100%" style="border-collapse: collapse; mso-table-lspace: 0pt; mso-table-rspace: 0pt; max-width: 600px;">
            <!-- Header -->
            <tr>
                <td align="center" style="padding: 30px 20px; background: linear-gradient(135deg, #0d47a1, #1565c0, #1976d2); text-align: center; color: #ffffff;">
                    <!-- Graduation Cap SVG Icon -->
                    <div style="font-size: 48px; margin: 15px 0; color: #ffd700;">
                        <svg width="70" height="70" viewBox="0 0 70 70" style="display: block; margin: 0 auto;">
                            <!-- Cap Base -->
                            <path d="M56.5,25.5L35,15L13.5,25.5L35,36L56.5,25.5z" fill="#ffd700" stroke="#ccac00" stroke-width="0.5"/>
                            <!-- Cap Top -->
                            <path d="M13.5,25.5L35,36L35,15L13.5,25.5z" fill="#e6c300" stroke="#ccac00" stroke-width="0.5"/>
                            <!-- Tassel Loop -->
                            <circle cx="35" cy="15" r="2.5" fill="#ccac00"/>
                            <!-- Tassel Cord -->
                            <path d="M35,15L35,45" stroke="#ccac00" stroke-width="1.5"/>
                            <!-- Tassel -->
                            <path d="M35,45L30,55L40,55L35,45z" fill="#ccac00"/>
                            <path d="M30,55L30,60L40,60L40,55" fill="#ccac00"/>
                        </svg>
                    </div>
                    <a href="#" style="font-size: 32px; font-weight: bold; text-decoration: none; color: #ffffff; display: inline-block; margin-bottom: 15px;">
                        UNIVERSITY OF RWANDA
                    </a>
                    <p style="margin: 0;">Department of Career Development & Corporate Relations</p>
                </td>
            </tr>

            <!-- Content -->
            <tr>
                <td style="padding: 40px 30px; line-height: 1.6; background-color: #ffffff;">
                    <h1 style="color: #0d47a1; font-size: 32px; font-weight: 700; margin-bottom: 20px; text-align: center; letter-spacing: 1.5px;">
                        Invitation to Our Graduation Ceremony
                    </h1>

                    <p style="color: #555555; font-size: 16px; margin-bottom: 25px;">
                        Dear <%= companyName %> Team,
                    </p>

                    <p style="color: #555555; font-size: 16px; margin-bottom: 25px;">
                        On behalf of the University of Rwanda, we are delighted to
                        extend a special invitation to your organization to attend our
                        <span style="color: #0d47a1; font-weight: 600;">2025 Graduation Ceremony</span>.
                    </p>

                    <p style="color: #555555; font-size: 16px; margin-bottom: 25px;">
                        This celebration marks the culmination of our students' academic
                        journey and represents an excellent opportunity for
                        <span style="color: #0d47a1; font-weight: 600;"><%= companyName %></span> to connect with our newest cohort of talented
                        graduates.
                    </p>

                    <div style="height: 3px; background: linear-gradient(to right, transparent, #1976d2, transparent); margin: 30px 0;"></div>

                    <div style="background-color: #f0f7ff; border-radius: 10px; padding: 25px; margin: 30px 0; border-left: 5px solid #1976d2;">
                        <h2 style="color: #0d47a1; font-size: 20px; font-weight: 600; margin-bottom: 15px; text-align: center;">
                            Event Details
                        </h2>

                        <div style="display: flex; margin-bottom: 12px;">
                            <div style="color: #1976d2; margin-right: 15px; font-size: 18px; min-width: 24px;">
                                <!-- Calendar Icon -->
                                <svg width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="#1976d2">
                                    <path d="M19,4h-1V2h-2v2H8V2H6v2H5C3.9,4,3,4.9,3,6v14c0,1.1,0.9,2,2,2h14c1.1,0,2-0.9,2-2V6C21,4.9,20.1,4,19,4z M19,20H5V9h14V20z"/>
                                    <rect x="7" y="11" width="2" height="2"/>
                                    <rect x="11" y="11" width="2" height="2"/>
                                    <rect x="15" y="11" width="2" height="2"/>
                                    <rect x="7" y="14" width="2" height="2"/>
                                    <rect x="11" y="14" width="2" height="2"/>
                                    <rect x="15" y="14" width="2" height="2"/>
                                </svg>
                            </div>
                            <div><strong>Date:</strong> Friday, October 10, 2025</div>
                        </div>

                        <div style="display: flex; margin-bottom: 12px;">
                            <div style="color: #1976d2; margin-right: 15px; font-size: 18px; min-width: 24px;">
                                <!-- Clock Icon -->
                                <svg width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="#1976d2">
                                    <path d="M12,2C6.5,2,2,6.5,2,12s4.5,10,10,10s10-4.5,10-10S17.5,2,12,2z M12,20c-4.4,0-8-3.6-8-8s3.6-8,8-8s8,3.6,8,8S16.4,20,12,20z"/>
                                    <polygon points="12.5,7 11,7 11,13 16.2,16.2 17,14.9 12.5,12.2"/>
                                </svg>
                            </div>
                            <div>
                                <strong>Time:</strong> 09:00 AM (Corporate registration begins at 08:30 AM)
                            </div>
                        </div>

                        <div style="display: flex; margin-bottom: 12px;">
                            <div style="color: #1976d2; margin-right: 15px; font-size: 18px; min-width: 24px;">
                                <!-- Location Icon -->
                                <svg width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="#1976d2">
                                    <path d="M12,2C8.1,2,5,5.1,5,9c0,5.3,7,13,7,13s7-7.8,7-13C19,5.1,15.9,2,12,2z M12,11.5c-1.4,0-2.5-1.1-2.5-2.5s1.1-2.5,2.5-2.5s2.5,1.1,2.5,2.5S13.4,11.5,12,11.5z"/>
                                </svg>
                            </div>
                            <div>
                                <strong>Location:</strong> Nyagahinga, Kabuga, Rwanda<br />123
                                KN 4 Ave, Kigali, Rwanda
                            </div>
                        </div>

                        <div style="display: flex; margin-bottom: 12px;">
                            <div style="color: #1976d2; margin-right: 15px; font-size: 18px; min-width: 24px;">
                                <!-- Chair Icon -->
                                <svg width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="#1976d2">
                                    <path d="M7,11v2h10v-2c0-1.86-1.27-3.43-3-3.87V5h1V3H9v2h1v2.13C8.27,7.57,7,9.14,7,11z"/>
                                    <path d="M20,13H4v-2H2v8h4v-4h12v4h4v-8h-2V13z"/>
                                </svg>
                            </div>
                            <div>
                                <strong>Seating:</strong> Reserved corporate section with premium viewing for <%= companyName %>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>

                    <a href="<%= rsvpLink %>" style="display: block; width: 250px; background: linear-gradient(to right, #4CAF50, #2E7D32); color: #ffffff; text-decoration: none; font-weight: 600; font-size: 16px; padding: 16px 0; text-align: center; border-radius: 50px; margin: 30px auto; box-shadow: 0 4px 15px rgba(76, 175, 80, 0.3);">
                        Accept Invitation
                    </a>

                    <p style="color: #555555; font-size: 16px; margin-bottom: 25px;">
                        We would be honored by <%= companyName %>'s presence at this momentous
                        occasion. Your participation not only celebrates our students'
                        achievements but also demonstrates your organization's commitment
                        to nurturing emerging talent.
                    </p>

                    <p style="color: #555555; font-size: 16px; margin-bottom: 25px;">
                        Sincerely,<br /><strong>Michael Johnson</strong><br />Director of
                        Corporate Relations<br />University of Rwanda
                    </p>
                </td>
            </tr>

            <!-- Footer -->
            <tr>
                <td style="background-color: #0d47a1; color: #ecf0f1; padding: 25px 30px; text-align: center; font-size: 14px;">
                    <div style="margin: 20px 0;">
                        <!-- Facebook Icon -->
                        <a href="#" style="display: inline-block; margin: 0 10px; color: #ffd700; text-decoration: none;">
